<text id="02-output-contract" title="pair-programming Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="500" depth="essential">
  <summary>Session protocol JSON schema.</summary>

  <section title="JSON Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/pair-programming",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["mode", "roster", "pomodoroMinutes", "sessionMdPath"],
  "properties": {
    "mode": {"enum": ["classic", "ping-pong", "strong-style", "tour-guide"]},
    "roster": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["name", "isAI"],
        "properties": {"name": {"type": "string"}, "isAI": {"type": "boolean"}}
      }
    },
    "pomodoroMinutes": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 20, "maximum": 30},
    "sessionMdPath": {"type": "string"},
    "humanIsDriverIfAINavigator": {"type": "boolean", "const": true}
  }
}]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "mode": "strong-style",
  "roster": [
    {"name": "Ruslan", "isAI": false},
    {"name": "Claude", "isAI": true}
  ],
  "pomodoroMinutes": 25,
  "sessionMdPath": "docs/sessions/2026-05-22.md",
  "humanIsDriverIfAINavigator": true
}]]></code>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "mode": "mix-of-all",
  "roster": [{"name": "Ruslan", "isAI": false}, {"name": "Claude", "isAI": true}],
  "pomodoroMinutes": 60,
  "humanIsDriverIfAINavigator": false
}]]></code>
      <note>3 violations: mode not in enum (r4), pomodoro 60min (r5), human not driver despite AI navigator (r2).</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>mode is one of the four canonical modes.</item>
      <item>If any roster member is AI, human is the driver.</item>
      <item>pomodoroMinutes in 20-30 range.</item>
      <item>sessionMdPath set; file will be appended on retro.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
